dmca.title: Text and Images DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google

works.description:
Text and all images of the stretching  
session have been created by Personal Trainer Toronto, with the assistance
 
of Think Basis Inc. The information provided is regarding Fascial  
Stretching and the method used. The photograph copied is of a woman in a  
black outfit on a stretching table getting stretched by a trainer in a  
white shirt. Her right leg is wrapped partially around the trainer's body.
